"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-football-best-players-paris-2024-b2585211.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The men's and women's events are under way ahead of the opening ceremony - with some star names on show  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  In the days leading up to Friday's official opening ceremony for the ParisOlympics, several of thelonger-running events are already up and running- including football in both men's and women's events.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the women have full international squads on show, men's teams are generally an under-23 event with up to three overage exceptions per squad - meaning a blend of some of the world's best and the most exciting up-and-coming youngsters across the entirety of Olympic football this summer.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here we have picked out 10 players whose performances and selections could define the football memories and medals atParis 2024.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Linda Caicedo, Colombia  Although the women's event is a senior competition, some of the greatest youngsters around are gathered in France this month - and Caicedo might be the best of them.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1082, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_Caicedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6353640252286768e-14, \"text\": \"Caicedo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_Caicedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_Caicedo\"}, {\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999806877897, \"rank\": 1.9312437502021788e-08, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3408795269174134e-24, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_Caicedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6353640252286768e-14, \"text\": \"Caicedo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_Caicedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felipe_Caicedo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still only 19, the Colombian forward starred at the World Cup last year, scored the goal of the tournament and earned a move to Real Madrid, where already she has won individual awards noting her as the best under-21 in the game.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3516591923348466e-30, \"text\": \"Real Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All this as a teenager... and four years after overcoming ovarian cancer.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's a standout in so many ways.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kadeisha Buchanan, Canada  From LaLiga to London, Buchanan is a Chelsea defender in the WSL and a star centre-back with Canada.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kadeisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kadeisha Buchanan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kadeisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kadeisha_Buchanan\"}, {\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999987453521, \"rank\": 1.2544554787618469e-09, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1638, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Liga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.105971325250813e-75, \"text\": \"LaLiga\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Liga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Liga\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999977992721711, \"rank\": 2.1989686597501654e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Buchanan\", \"score\": 0.999986880014269, \"rank\": 1.311964223240694e-05, \"text\": \"Buchanan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Buchanan\"}, {\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999839242265, \"rank\": 1.6075869886071543e-08, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 0.9150013292883211, \"rank\": 0.09289400146838735, \"text\": \"WSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999987453521, \"rank\": 1.2544554787618469e-09, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At age 28, she's set to win her 150th senior cap for the national team during the Games and will be a key part of their hopes to progress from a very competitive group, which includes the hosts and the aforementioned Colombia.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999806877897, \"rank\": 1.9312437502021788e-08, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was harshly sent off in the Uefa Women's Champions League semi-final second leg which tilted the game the way of Barcelona - the Olympics is a great stage for her to put that behind her and show her qualities.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2078, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0830916978654733e-27, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jaedyn Shaw, USA  It's no secret that Emma Hayes has begun her USWNT revolution with the huge decision of leaving aside legend Alex Morgan - which means the spotlight will naturally shift to those selected ahead of her.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2189, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.5468308954561567, \"rank\": 0.8287189116585326, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Hayes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most intriguing among them might be record-breaking teenager Jaedyn Shaw, not just a prospect for the national team but also a clubmate of Morgan's at San Diego Wave.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2464, \"end\": 2468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.499693390094626e-13, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}, {\"begin\": 2535, \"end\": 2541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_le_Fay\", \"score\": 0.9814774904155095, \"rank\": 0.01877132781253382, \"text\": \"Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_le_Fay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_le_Fay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 19-year-old has seven goals already for the USA's senior side and last year broke the NWSL record for most goals scored as a teen.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.5468308954561567, \"rank\": 0.8287189116585326, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2653, \"end\": 2657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4162286331193057e-21, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Versatile, two-footed and technically gifted, Shaw could be a wildcard to send Hayes and Co toward the medals.\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2744, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.499693390094626e-13, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marta, Brazil  From one end of a career to the other, Brazilian legend Marta is one of the biggest names in the game of all time.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2817, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8532167223119413e-16, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now aged 38, the six-time World Player of the Year will play at her sixth Olympic Games and will set a new record if she scores at them - she was already the first footballer to score at five.\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Given she has already announced she will retire from international football at the end of Paris 2024, it's sure to be an emotional departure either way after almost 200 caps and, so far, 119 goals.\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aitana Bonmati, Spain  After the greatest of all time, it's also fair to point out we have the greatest of the current time at the Summer Games, with Spain's Bonmati the reigning Ballon d'Or Feminin holder, the Fifa Best Women's Player holder, the winner of last summer's World Cup Golden Ball award and this year's Laureus World Sportswoman of the Year.\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3332, \"end\": 3346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana_Bonmat\\u00ed\", \"score\": 0.9999999905639925, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aitana Bonmati\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana_Bonmat\\u00ed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aitana_Bonmat\\u00ed\"}, {\"begin\": 3348, \"end\": 3353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998744897, \"rank\": 1.2555104068872102e-10, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3482, \"end\": 3487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998744897, \"rank\": 1.2555104068872102e-10, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3511, \"end\": 3522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ballon_d'Or\", \"score\": 0.9999999995993676, \"rank\": 4.0043662620405886e-10, \"text\": \"Ballon d'Or\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ballon_d'Or\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ballon_d'Or\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been quite the 12 months for the Barcelona superstar and Olympic gold would be some way to cap it off - if La Roja are to go the distance and add this medal to last year's triumph, her performances in midfield will be key.\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3727, \"end\": 3736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0830916978654733e-27, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Olise, France  Over to the men and mostly a collection of the under-23 options.\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 4005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3918, \"end\": 3931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Olise\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\"}, {\"begin\": 3933, \"end\": 3939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3408795269174134e-24, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having represented England at youth level, Olise has now departed those shores entirely: Bayern Munich at club level with a massive transfer this summer, and France on the international stage.\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4164, \"end\": 4170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3408795269174134e-24, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's set to be a key player for them at the Olympics, which will really be a first glimpse of him playing among the elite following his time with Crystal Palace.\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no doubting his quality or ability to impact matches - but it will be all eyes on him now with Les Bleus and as a \\u00a350m player.\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's made a good start, mind,with a goal in the opening 3-0 win over USA.\", \"from\": 4497, \"to\": 4570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4566, \"end\": 4569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.5468308954561567, \"rank\": 0.8287189116585326, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Julian Alvarez, Argentina  Our one selection for overage players is still only 24: Man City's Alvarez, who reportedly requested he be allowed to play in this tournament having also played a full part at the Copa America this month.\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4588, \"end\": 4597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.483771876813771e-13, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4655, \"end\": 4663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9118363601088867e-14, \"text\": \"Man City\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Argentina's start wasa disappointing one in a chaotic 2-1 defeat to Morocco, Alvarez will need to show his leadership qualities as much as his goalscoring prowess to help the South Americans through to the latter stages.\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 5027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4807, \"end\": 4816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.483771876813771e-13, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4875, \"end\": 4882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.78176940960264e-19, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fermin Lopez, Spain  Also at Euro 2024 but only used as a substitute once, Barcelona attacking midfielder Lopez will expect to play a much more fulsome role at the Olympics for Spain.\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5029, \"end\": 5035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.097620731024514e-16, \"text\": \"Fermin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\"}, {\"begin\": 5036, \"end\": 5041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.9953709621259313, \"rank\": 0.0046505257930867655, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\"}, {\"begin\": 5043, \"end\": 5048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998744897, \"rank\": 1.2555104068872102e-10, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5104, \"end\": 5113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0830916978654733e-27, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}, {\"begin\": 5135, \"end\": 5140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.9953709621259313, \"rank\": 0.0046505257930867655, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\"}, {\"begin\": 5206, \"end\": 5211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998744897, \"rank\": 1.2555104068872102e-10, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With tremendous movement and an ability to pick a pass in crowded areas or get early shots away, he's proven a vital tool for unlocking defences at club level - if he can transfer that to the international stage he will be a huge weapon against the deep defences that La Roja face so often.\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Joel Chima Fujita, Japan  The starting pair of Japanese midfielders are clubmates in Belgium for Sint-Truiden - but it's Fujita, born in Tokyo to a Nigerian father and Japanese mother, who looks a huge prospect.\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5524, \"end\": 5529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9896193081443698, \"rank\": 0.01048958096318669, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5590, \"end\": 5597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.252664898737362e-23, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5642, \"end\": 5647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997476959087074, \"rank\": 0.00025236732564455356, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 5653, \"end\": 5661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6737589490262986e-15, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has played for the senior side a couple of times and, with a solid campaign in Belgium behind him last time out, is primed for a big step forward over the coming year or two.\", \"from\": 5717, \"to\": 5894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5799, \"end\": 5806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.252664898737362e-23, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fujita is captaining the side at the Games, even with a few older players than him involved, and the signs are good as he impressed in a 5-0 thrashing of Paraguay in their opener.\", \"from\": 5895, \"to\": 6074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6049, \"end\": 6057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8615696860170553e-21, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ilaix Moriba, Guinea  Finally, we turn to Guinea and a player who earned a big name early on but has stuttered somewhat since: Moriba, formerly of Barcelona, now with RB Leipzig but with a couple of not-entirely-impressive loan spells behind him over the last couple of years.\", \"from\": 6076, \"to\": 6352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6076, \"end\": 6088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilaix_Moriba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ilaix Moriba\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilaix_Moriba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilaix_Moriba\"}, {\"begin\": 6223, \"end\": 6232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0830916978654733e-27, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}, {\"begin\": 6243, \"end\": 6253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RB_Leipzig\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4531421138205725e-34, \"text\": \"RB Leipzig\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RB_Leipzig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RB_Leipzig\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At his best early on he was a striding, ball-carrying, creative hub who could play high upfield from midfield and join the attack late on.\", \"from\": 6353, \"to\": 6491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still only 21, Moriba has the blend of technical quality and athleticism to make him tough to stop when on form - finding his level in Paris would be a big boost to getting a promising career back on track, though an opening 2-1 loss to New Zealand leaves the National Elephants up against it.\", \"from\": 6492, \"to\": 6785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6627, \"end\": 6632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0191809066291774e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 6729, \"end\": 6740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9980966344132997, \"rank\": 0.0019069952062540638, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 6787, \"to\": 7017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6838, \"end\": 6849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.128893986487731e-19, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"